  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Tangent has period &pi;. 73&pi;/6 = 12&pi; + &pi;/6 = 12&pi; + &pi;/6, so tan(73&pi;/6) = tan(&pi;/6) = &radic;3/3.</p><p>Choice A is &minus;tan(2&pi;/3). Choices B and D use the wrong reference angle or sign.</p>",
